HEADWORD: Bobby
<hw>Bob"by</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A nickname for a
British policeman; -- from <person>Sir <etsep>Robert</etsep>
Peel</person>, who remodeled the police force. See
<er>Peeler</er>.</def> <mark>[Slang, Eng.]</mark>
<rj><au>Dickens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

